creator: Element Mobile Development
descriptionHtml:
Create original logos and designs using thousands of free graphic elements and editing options.
Our Application provides a very convenient and easy interface to create a logo for your brand
or you can use our templates just change the name and done! your logo is ready.
Adding texture, picture from a gallery, and gradient to mask logo or text is very easy just select the logo and use gradient or what you want from the given options apply it to logo or text to get the extra 3D look to your logo or text.
Fill logo or vector shapes using texture, simple colors or even a picture from your gallery
save the logo as a draft if you want to edit later or just complete the work that's your choice our app is very easy for the user you don't have to be a professional to use our app everyone can use and create logos of their choice just use your imagination and create unlimited logos.
Features
*3D rotation for logos and text
*3D depth to text or logos
*apply texture color or pictures from the gallery into text or logo (for masking purpose)
*save as a draft to edit it later
*Unlimited Backgrounds of different types Like Gradient Background Color Background Or 3d Backgrounds
*30 Categories of logos including 3D logos to create logos for gaming
*Apply Shadow effect to text or logo and you can change the shadow color as you see fit
*change the angle and depth of the shadow
*Use Predefined shapes for creating different graphics like creating Facebook banner WhatsApp sticker LinkedIn banner, Pinterest pin and many more you can see the shapes and templates example in screenshots
*Capture and Edit Logos
*Curve Text
*Pick Colors
_______________________________________________________________________________________
If any problem occurs or you need a new feature then please feel free to contact me on my email. I am a solo developer.
Send Feedback and I will provide what every you people want in a logo maker app Thanks. :)
